Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.19,0:00:05.82,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,{*}Excuse me...{*Um, Sensei?}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.13,0:00:07.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.71,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,I have a question...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.18,0:00:15.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, this formula here?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You've got the right approach. You just—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.08,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.08,0:00:22.40,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,After much consideration,\nI've decided I need to stay by your side after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.40,0:00:24.13,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You need my support!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.13,0:00:27.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We've been over this. I'm perfectly fine\nteaching a class on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Now hurry back to your classroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.29,0:00:31.18,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be sneaking out of class.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.18,0:00:32.14,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.41,0:00:35.79,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.23,0:00:40.31,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,How many times do I have\nto teach you this lesson?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.44,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.43,0:00:43.48,Default,Catherine,0,0,60,,{=5}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.48,0:00:43.52,Default,Catherine,0,0,-34,,{=5}{\fscy80}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.52,0:00:43.56,Default,Catherine,0,0,-60,,{=5}{\fscx98\fscy78}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.60,0:00:43.64,Default,Catherine,0,0,-68,,{=5}{\fscx120\fscy84}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.64,0:00:43.69,Default,Catherine,0,0,-108,,{=5}{\fscx120\fscy84}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.73,0:00:43.77,Default,Catherine,0,0,33,,{=5}{\fscx85\fscy160}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.77,0:00:43.81,Default,Catherine,0,0,48,,{=5}{\fscx85\fscy160}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.81,0:00:43.85,Default,Catherine,0,0,51,,{=5}{\fscx88.75\fscy125}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.85,0:00:43.89,Default,Catherine,0,0,43,,{=5}{\fscx88.75\fscy125}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.89,0:00:43.94,Default,Catherine,0,0,57,,{=5}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.94,0:00:44.31,Default,Catherine,0,0,51,,{=5}The elementary schoolers\nare in the next room over!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.85,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.36,0:00:52.03,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I have to say, I never expected Natsu{**-kun}\nto volunteer to be our teacher.
Comment: 10,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.05,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,And for high schoolers, at that.
Comment: 10,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.87,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Dude's barely any older than the rest of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.03,0:00:56.87,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,And for high schoolers, at that.\nDude's barely any older than the rest of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.39,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,He's a smart cookie, after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.83,0:01:01.00,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Don't forget he even went to the Academy!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.00,0:01:03.67,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yeah, our little rocket scientist\nis the talk of the whole town.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.67,0:01:04.45,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.45,0:01:06.37,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Honestly, you should hear some of the gossip.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.37,0:01:10.96,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,People can't shut up about the handsome\nyoung man who's just started teaching here.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.96,0:01:12.83,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Case in point: Exhibit A over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.85,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Can you, like, get off your high horse?\nNobody cares that you've been here longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.85,0:01:19.00,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Why'd you start showing up then?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.07,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.07,0:01:24.41,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I just came here to check things out\n'cause I heard the electricity was back, okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.41,0:01:25.65,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Come here to {\i1}learn{\i0} next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.65,0:01:27.36,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Nobody asked.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.36,0:01:30.74,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,But anyway, that's my story.\nMy name's Youko.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.04,0:01:33.57,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ah, of course. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.57,0:01:37.37,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I heard you were working all by yourself\nto get the school back up and running!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.37,0:01:41.13,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You have any problems, you come to me.\nI'll be a lot more useful than this bozo.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.13,0:01:45.62,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Just to set the record straight,\nme and Natsu built that generator {\i1}together,{\i0} got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.83,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.83,0:01:50.34,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,We all know you were just his gofer.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.67,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Like hell I was!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.96,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You {\i1}suuure{\i0} about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.59,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What, you think I'm stupid, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.28,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Oops, did I say that part out loud? {!}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Just a little farther...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{\an8}For the millionth time, don't talk underwater.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.34,0:03:41.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A cable...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Probably just some old TV\nor internet infrastructure, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.13,0:03:50.77,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,One more block, and you should see\na house with a chimney.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.77,0:03:51.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.25,0:03:57.52,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I never thought we'd be able to\nstart up a salvaging service.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.52,0:04:03.10,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Plenty of folks have sentimental items\nthey left behind in their old sunken homes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.98,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,More importantly, shouldn't you\nshoot your shot soon?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.98,0:04:06.85,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.14,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,For Natsu!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.35,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hwuh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.11,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You seriously thought I wouldn't notice?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.55,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Keep stalling any longer,\nand someone else'll snatch him up!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.21,0:04:19.82,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Youko says even more girls\nare gonna start showing up next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.39,0:04:24.10,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,More students at school is a good thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.85,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,{*}Ms. Hana{*Hana-chan-sensei} is even teaching the younger kids for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.85,0:04:29.01,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,That's not my point, and you know it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.01,0:04:29.46,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.08,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Don't you want to be with Natsu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.76,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,As more than friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's gotta be it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't hear—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.25,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Tasty things make you happy, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.69,Default,Ishige,0,0,0,,Oh, you really found it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.74,Default,Ishige,0,0,0,,Thank you kindly.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.51,0:05:00.82,Default,Ishige,0,0,0,,It isn't much,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.99,Default,Ishige,0,0,0,,but here's a token of my appreciation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.41,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-That's{\i0} our payment?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.29,0:05:07.33,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh, see...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.33,0:05:10.29,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,We have certain prices for our services...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.79,0:05:12.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thank you. We'll gladly accept.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri, can you carry these?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.49,0:05:19.76,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.81,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Dude thinks we're running\na damn charity over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Something's fishy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.39,0:05:24.78,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.18,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.61,0:05:29.30,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san} was smiling.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.14,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Just now, and when we were underwater, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.44,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,And that's fishy?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.19,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.69,0:05:40.57,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,A little while ago, nothing could get him to smile.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.57,0:05:43.21,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Hey, I mean, can you blame the guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.21,0:05:48.11,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Our strapping young teacher's got\nevery girl in town making googly-eyes at him.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.15,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,It's like he's got his own personal harem.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.41,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Harem...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.75,0:05:57.46,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Searching, searching...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.46,Alt,Atri,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}, wai—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.46,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,N-N-N—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}, you horndog!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.53,0:06:04.09,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,This calls for a rocket punching!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.30,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hwuh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.94,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.94,0:06:11.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,It's not like that! It's just not!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.60,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.60,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ryuu{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.00,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't know. Maybe it {\i1}is{\i0} like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.00,0:06:17.69,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.69,0:06:22.45,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,When guys are riding high on cloud nine like this,\nthat's your best chance at knocking 'em down.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.95,0:06:23.99,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Knock them down?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.66,0:06:28.77,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Natsu usually doesn't even spare\nany girl a second look, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.77,0:06:31.41,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You're looking at\nthe chance of a lifetime right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.25,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,To what, punish him by\nknocking him down into the sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.98,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'd want to go {\i1}that{\i0} far.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.68,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,He can't swim, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.74,0:06:43.69,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.80,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,How 'bout you give me a hand taking\nthese watermelons over to Ririka and the kids?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.45,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Now look...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.45,0:06:54.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I can't afford to leave Natsuki{**-san}'s side.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.09,0:06:56.81,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsu!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.50,0:07:01.27,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Can I borrow Atri to help\ntake these watermelons to the kids?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sure! Go along with Ryuuji, Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.31,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh? But I—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Master's orders!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.47,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Hup...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.89,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Well, if I must...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.56,0:07:15.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm sure the kids will be very happy at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Gonna need to replace those hatch parts soon...\nIt won't hold up for too many more dives.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.93,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}, want me to get\ndinner started while Atri's out?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You'd do that? Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.34,0:07:42.39,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Promise you'll let her take care of\nthe cooking someday, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.82,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'm teaching her everything I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Who, Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.23,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.25,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She really wants your approval.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.70,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Just the other day, I taught her how to make nikujaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri can make nikujaga...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.06,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What do you think of Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.99,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Well, hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.99,0:08:06.55,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She's a nice girl. A real cutie...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.55,0:08:09.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, uh, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Remember what you were saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How she doesn't feel like a robot at all?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.25,0:08:16.06,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't think a robot could smile like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.98,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Her happiness looks like it\nreally comes from the heart!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Maybe she really does
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.14,0:08:27.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,have a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.21,0:08:35.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The first-ever Humanoid running an AI\ncapable of real human emotions...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You think that's what she is?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.19,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And it's not like I could prove it either way.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.98,0:08:47.69,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But if that's what she is, it'd explain everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.51,0:08:52.42,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why Grandma preserved her\nso carefully in that capsule...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why her manufacturer tried to recall her...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.27,0:09:03.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Remember when we turned on\nthe lights in the school?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.58,0:09:06.25,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,When I saw her smile back then, it made me think.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If she really can experience happiness,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,if she really is smiling from the heart,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.91,0:09:16.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,then I have to start treating her like a human. {? tricky, should discuss}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.11,0:09:22.89,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.11,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,All right kiddos, dig in!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.67,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Eat up while it's still nice and cold, you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.51,Default,Ririka; Toru; Miyo,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.59,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,It's so sweet!
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,{I didn't add these lines, and I don't think anything is missing. -Pik}{i think these are the background lines? -p}
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,On Top,Miyo,0,0,0,,{I didn't add these lines, and I don't think anything is missing. -Pik}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.77,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there. Go get some for yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.05,0:09:44.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{*}Très bien{*Delicious}!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.64,0:09:53.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I love Minamo so much! This is great!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.20,0:09:56.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,For someone who doesn't need food,\nyou sure can put away a lot of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.89,0:10:01.05,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\q2}My highly discerning taste buds allow me\nto prioritize consuming food with the optimal flavor.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.05,0:10:04.08,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Once again, proof positive of my sky-high specs!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.94,0:10:08.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Here's hoping that functionality comes in handy\nfor cooking something decent.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.96,0:10:11.45,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san} has {\i1}hopes{\i0} for me...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.38,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You can expect great things!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}expecting{\i0} nothing but disappointment.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.60,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Hwuh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.47,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,He's not?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.86,0:10:19.74,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.74,0:10:25.75,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}'s recent good mood\ndoesn't have anything to do with girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.48,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Then what gives?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.36,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Apparently... it's all because of Atri{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.78,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.96,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Wait, is that guy into—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.68,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You're kidding! She's a Humanoid!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.64,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,She's a robot!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.62,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.62,0:10:44.41,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'm sure he doesn't think about her like {\i1}that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.58,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Then what {\i1}is{\i0} he thinking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.38,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hmm, how do I put this...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.40,0:10:56.80,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I don't think Natsu{**-kun}'s interested\nin romance right now... Not with anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What're you writing?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.94,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No looking!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.94,0:11:10.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What, your logs?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'd figure your master\nought to have the right to see those.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.58,0:11:17.68,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Well, I'm of the understanding\nthat a girl's diary is meant to be private!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.57,0:11:24.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,"When I told him he couldn't look,\nNatsuki{**-san} got all pouty."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.21,0:11:24.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop writing nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.85,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Why, it isn't nonsense at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.35,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's an objective record of events as they happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Safely storing my logbook.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.43,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's very important.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.43,0:11:40.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Just lower your skirt already!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.05,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Why so bashful?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.32,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's nothing you don't see\nwhenever we sleep together.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It comes off different depending on\nhow you show it, okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.61,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I see. I've updated my mental model.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.40,0:11:55.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I swear... Maybe she really\ndoesn't have emotions after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.63,0:12:01.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, even humans have to learn to develop\na sense of shame as they grow up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Maybe she just has the mind of a chi—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Nothing. I just thought I'd like to see\nmore of your cute blushing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's it! You get your ass\ninto the bath right this minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.97,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Stop it! Robot harassment!\nRobot harassment, I say!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.34,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.15,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.15,0:12:30.71,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Minamo seems to think\nhe's not interested in romance,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.15,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,but what's your read?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.69,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Uh, hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.19,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I dunno. I haven't talked to him that much.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.32,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,But if anyone knows...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.45,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,That kiddo's love life?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.55,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.88,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,We wanted to hear an adult's perspective.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.66,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Well, kid's got plenty of book smarts,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.51,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,but he seems like a real late bloomer\nwhen it comes to romance...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.51,0:12:55.34,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,So you think Minamo's right about him\nnot being interested in that stuff?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.24,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.05,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.05,0:13:02.54,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,If you ask me, it sounds a lot more like\nhe's already got his heart set on someone!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.85,Default,Yoko and Ryuji,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.85,0:13:06.48,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,He went to the Academy, didn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.48,0:13:09.43,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Maybe he already met his special someone there.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.77,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,That's what I'm reading from\nhow calm he's always acting, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.32,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,I oughta ask him straight. Man to man.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.50,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Pfft, no shot!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.50,0:13:20.39,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,As if he'd spill the beans\nif {\i1}you{\i0} were the one asking!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.39,0:13:21.49,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,And why the hell not?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.12,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Girl's got a point.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.12,0:13:26.83,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,It's easier to talk about\nthis sorta stuff with the opposite sex.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.83,0:13:27.91,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,So what do we do then?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.94,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Guess I'll have to lend you a little hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.94,0:13:34.42,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,A teacher really shouldn't be\nprying into her students' love lives,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.38,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,but hey, a fellow teacher is totally fair game.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.88,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You'll help us?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.50,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,So, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.12,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Trust me. It'll be a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.12,0:13:43.15,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Now listen closely...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.72,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Mumble mumble, whisper whisper...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.06,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Huh?! I have to {\i1}what?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.06,0:13:52.05,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Got it? You've gotta make him think\nyou're dead serious, you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.05,0:13:55.18,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I expect you to be able to nail\nthe delivery by next Sunday!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.57,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,No waaay!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.45,0:14:00.07,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Someone, please, kill me already...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.57,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh, guess I'll be\non the sidelines for this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.99,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,This doesn't look like Tak{*}ky{*-kun} at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.84,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Aw, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,We'll have him looking\ngood as new in no time, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.67,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's in an advanced state of deterioration.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.67,0:14:18.17,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I would imagine this plushie is fit only for disposal.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.01,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,We're so sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.48,0:14:25.87,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Ain't easy being a salvager, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.87,0:14:28.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can't expect everything we recover\nto still be in good condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.72,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Should we hike our rates?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.72,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Considering how much labor we're putting in,\nwe'll be making a loss at our current prices.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Nah, no need.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.07,0:14:39.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,As long as we can make the islanders happy,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,it's a job well worth doing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That said,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.62,0:14:51.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,we can't exactly pay for fuel with goodwill alone...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.61,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Natsuki{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.50,0:15:01.38,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,{*}You don't mind if I call you that... do you?{*Natsuki-sensei... Am I allowed to call you that?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.32,0:15:02.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.79,0:15:06.84,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Y-Youko! I'm a student in your class!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, the one who showed up a little while ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.51,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.99,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,See, there's something\nI just {\i1}had{\i0} to ask you about...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.42,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I hope I'm not bothering you or anything...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.42,0:15:19.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, the formula we covered the other day?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You start by factoring the—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.19,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.35,0:15:28.72,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,{*}I... I{*Sensei, I...} love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.81,0:15:37.75,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,{*}I meant it{*Sensei}! Do you already have someone else?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.81,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Is it Minamo{**-chan}? It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.81,0:15:40.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Minamo?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.10,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,It's not her?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then is it that glasses girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Where'd that even come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.09,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Then is it...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.64,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,For one, Atri's a Humanoid...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Plus she barely looks ten years old! {the gaiken line, sort of tricky, not sure how to avoid overtranslation}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.82,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,But I've heard you can't sleep\nunless you're cuddling her...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.77,0:16:04.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She told you about that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.78,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Wait wha—it's actually {\i1}true?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,N-No, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.07,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,O-Of course I'm not into—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.20,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.95,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Then who is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.45,0:16:18.08,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Word of advice from someone\nwho's taught a lot longer than you have.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.22,0:16:22.34,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Times like this, you need to\ngrow a pair and tell it to 'em straight.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.76,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,An older girl from his childhood?{damn he has an adult woman fetish? -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.22,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,That's who Natsu{**-kun} likes?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.54,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.54,0:16:33.33,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Can't forget her, apparently.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.73,0:16:37.68,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Holy crap, that dork is too pure for this world!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.81,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Still, she was his first love? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.25,0:16:43.42,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I think he said it was when he was nine or so...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.57,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,It was right after he had his accident,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.82,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,and he was going through a lot mentally...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.75,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,And this girl showed up\nat just the right time to save his life.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I never knew...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.01,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Apparently this girl was maybe\nfive years older than him?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.29,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What's her name?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.64,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,And where is she now?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.57,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,That's the thing, he doesn't have a clue!\nNot even what her name was.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.25,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.41,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Does he remember any identifying features?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.02,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Her hair color? What she was wearing?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.02,0:17:24.46,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,A girl older by about five years, silky smooth hair,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.46,0:17:27.15,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,eyes as red as rubies...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.86,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,He was nine at the time,\nso if this chick was five years older...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.32,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Well, she'd be in her twenties by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.32,0:17:35.70,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Silky smooth hair, bright red eyes...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.84,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like anyo—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.84,0:17:38.79,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Gooood morning everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.37,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.00,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Silky smooth hair...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.42,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Bright red eyes...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.30,Default,Yokoo,0,0,0,,But she ain't twenty.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.30,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But she {\i1}is{\i0} a Humanoid!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.89,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Wh-What's all this about?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.89,0:17:57.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I have very important places to be,\nnamely Natsuki{**-san}'s side!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.85,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,This is important! Please tell us the truth, okay? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.94,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You've actually met Natsu before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.94,0:18:03.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.06,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.06,0:18:08.32,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah! When he was just a little boy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.81,0:18:18.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm afraid the relevant memory data is still missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.70,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But given how unreasonably high-spec I am,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.20,0:18:28.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,assuming what you're saying is true,\nit should only be a matter of time before I—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.57,0:18:32.57,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Piano?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.25,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.82,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Atri{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.60,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help, kiddo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.60,0:19:10.58,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,My piano playing ain't worth\na whistle compared to yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Nah. This is the only piece I even know how to play.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.22,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Well, it's a good one.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.89,0:19:17.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Someone really important to me always loved it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.20,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right, kiddos! Time to move our desks back!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.65,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll start class right after!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.43,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Where've you been this whole time?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop cutting class, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Master's orders.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.02,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.98,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu{**-kun}, your first crush...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wha—I told you to keep that between us!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.05,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, funny story...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.05,0:19:51.04,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Don't you think that girl might have been Atri{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.49,0:19:52.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.15,0:19:59.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Come on, that's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.27,0:20:01.14,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.98,0:20:05.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That girl was nothing like Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She was so much more composed...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Graceful. Gentle.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The kind where just being next to her would... {really interesting line, very neat take on your part!}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Come on. We've got class, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.41,0:20:22.62,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.29,0:20:25.16,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,I'll be back with dinner later!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.26,0:20:29.38,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ririka{**-chan} stays up reading late\ninto the night every day, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.38,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,She says she wants to be just like Natsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.67,0:20:33.53,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,To go to the Academy one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Not like I ever graduated, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.59,0:20:36.72,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.03,0:20:39.18,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Be the sort of role model she can look up to.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.85,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,She needs someone like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.62,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.62,0:20:52.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You okay? You didn't even say goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.53,0:20:59.75,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.03,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.04,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.67,0:21:33.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I sit on the sill to feel the rain.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.64,0:21:45.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{\t(8121,9914,0.8,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}And out comes the song I haven't sang in ages.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.58,0:21:52.08,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,This lost girl you saved\nwants her heart to be known.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.08,0:21:57.17,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ever grateful, and even when...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.17,0:22:00.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Our time has to end.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.29,0:22:06.34,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,{=11}It's been so long, Natsuki{**-san}!

